name: MACHINA 01 - Forbidden Creation // V2. Annihilation
description:
From the "MACHINA Limited Series"

"He stood there in silence, witnessing a corrupted marvel that could change the state of mankind, forever. The only question he wondered was, will this power if rid of chaos, offer true freedom or will it entail a different kind of slavery, first to a system ruled by people and now to the dictating Machina. "
